{"type":"tool_use","timestamp":1775897914304,"sessionID":"ses_2843cba31ffeB5jipUyIoDGq0I","part":{"id":"prt_d7bc3a7a100125ExxRg2g7dOCv","messageID":"msg_d7bc38ef1001tJX5AWujI7CRX7","sessionID":"ses_2843cba31ffeB5jipUyIoDGq0I","type":"tool","tool":"read","callID":"call_67f00fa42dbf4bae943c19ec","state":{"status":"completed","input":{"filePath":"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/delta-spec.md"},"output":"<path>/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/delta-spec.md</path>\n<type>file</type>\n<content>\n1: # AR-038: Go 单元测试 (workloadmanager) — Delta Spec\n2: \n3: ## Context\n4: \n5: - **Module:** `pkg/workloadmanager`\n6: - **Language:** Go\n7: - **Size:** L\n8: - **Base specs:** `deployment/client-go.md`\n9: \n10: ## Scope\n11: \n12: This delta spec defines the unit test coverage gaps for the `pkg/workloadmanager` module. Existing tests cover `handler/sandbox_delete_test.go`, `handler/sandbox_lifecycle_test.go`, `reconciler/metrics_test.go`, and `response/response_test.go`. This spec covers the **untested** code paths.\n13: \n14: ---\n15: \n16: ## R-1: Sandbox 创建 — AgentRuntime\n17: \n18: **Scope:** `handler/sandbox_create.go` — `CreateAgentRuntimeSandbox`, `buildAgentRuntimeSandboxCR`, `rollbackCR`, `generateSessionID`, `generateSandboxName`, `RandString`, `getPortsOrDefaults`, `buildEntryPoints`, `injectPicodAuthEnv`, `resolvePodIP`\n19: \n20: ### Requirement: CreateAgentRuntimeSandbox 成功路径\n21: \n22: #### Scenario: 成功创建 AgentRuntime Sandbox\n23: \n24: - **GIVEN** 有效的 CreateSandboxRequest（Kind=\"AgentRuntime\", Name, Namespace 已填）\n25:   AND DynamicClient 已配置\n26:   AND AgentRuntime CR 模板存在于目标 namespace\n27:   AND Store 可写\n28:   AND Reconciler.WatchSandboxOnce 可正常返回 channel\n29: - **WHEN** `CreateAgentRuntimeSandbox(c *gin.Context)` 被调用\n30: - **THEN** 返回 HTTP 201\n31:   AND 响应体包含 SessionID, SandboxID, SandboxName, EntryPoints\n32:   AND AgentRuntime CR 已创建到集群\n33:   AND Sandbox 信息已持久化到 Store\n34:   AND 响应中 EntryPoints 包含从 PodIP + TargetPorts 构建的 endpoint 列表\n35: \n36: ### Requirement: CreateAgentRuntimeSandbox 校验失败\n37: \n38: #### Scenario: 请求体 JSON 解析失败\n39: \n40: - **GIVEN** 请求体为非法 JSON\n41: - **WHEN** `CreateAgentRuntimeSandbox` 被调用\n42: - **THEN** 返回 HTTP 400\n43:   AND 响应包含 JSON 解析错误信息\n44: \n45: #### Scenario: 请求体校验失败 — 缺少必填字段\n46: \n47: - **GIVEN** CreateSandboxRequest 缺少 Name 或 Namespace\n48: - **WHEN** `CreateAgentRuntimeSandbox` 被调用\n49: - **THEN** 返回 HTTP 400\n50:   AND 响应包含校验失败信息\n51:   AND 未创建任何 CR\n52:   AND Store 未被写入\n53: \n54: ### Requirement: CreateAgentRuntimeSandbox 模板不存在\n55: \n56: #### Scenario: AgentRuntime 模板未找到\n57: \n58: - **GIVEN** 有效的 CreateSandboxRequest\n59:   AND 目标 namespace 中不存在匹配的 AgentRuntime CR 模板\n60: - **WHEN** `CreateAgentRuntimeSandbox` 被调用\n61: - **THEN** 返回 HTTP 404\n62:   AND 响应体包含 \"agent runtime template not found\" 类错误\n63:   AND 未创建 Sandbox CR\n64: \n65: ### Requirement: CreateAgentRuntimeSandbox CR 创建失败自动回滚\n66: \n67: #### Scenario: Sandbox CR 创建失败触发回滚\n68: \n69: - **GIVEN** AgentRuntime 模板存在\n70:   AND 动态客户端在创建 Sandbox CR 时返回错误（如网络不可达）\n71: - **WHEN** `CreateAgentRuntimeSandbox` 被调用\n72: - **THEN** 返回 HTTP 500\n73:   AND 已创建的 AgentRuntime CR 被 `rollbackCR` 清理\n74:   AND Store 中无残留记录\n75: \n76: ### Requirement: buildAgentRuntimeSandboxCR 注入元数据\n77: \n78: #### Scenario: CR 构建包含所有必需 label 和 annotation\n79: \n80: - **GIVEN** AgentRuntime 模板 CR\n81:   AND sessionID, sandboxName, workloadName, namespace 已生成\n82: - **WHEN** `buildAgentRuntimeSandboxCR` 被调用\n83: - **THEN** 返回 unstructured CR 对象\n84:   AND `metadata.labels` 包含 `app.kubernetes.io/managed-by`, `runtime.agentcube.io/session-id`, `runtime.agentcube.io/workload-name`, `runtime.agentcube.io/sandbox-name`\n85:   AND `metadata.annotations` 包含 `last-activity-time`\n86:   AND spec 从模板正确复制\n87: \n88: ### Requirement: generateSessionID 生成 UUID\n89: \n90: #### Scenario: 生成唯一 session ID\n91: \n92: - **GIVEN** 无\n93: - **WHEN** `generateSessionID()` 被调用\n94: - **THEN** 返回非空字符串\n95:   AND 多次调用返回值不同\n96:   AND 格式符合 UUID 规范\n97: \n98: ### Requirement: generateSandboxName 命名规则\n99: \n100: #### Scenario: sandbox 名称格式\n101: \n102: - **GIVEN** `workloadName = \"my-workload\"`\n103: - **WHEN** `generateSandboxName(workloadName)` 被调用\n104: - **THEN** 返回 `\"my-workload-<随机后缀>\"`\n105:   AND 总长度 ≤ 63 字符（Kubernetes name 限制）\n106:   AND 后缀为小写字母+数字\n107: \n108: ### Requirement: getPortsOrDefaults 端口回退\n109: \n110: #### Scenario: 空端口列表使用默认值\n111: \n112: - **GIVEN** 空的 TargetPort 列表\n113: - **WHEN** `getPortsOrDefaults(ports)` 被调用\n114: - **THEN** 返回包含默认端口 8080 的列表\n115:   AND protocol 为 TCP\n116: \n117: #### Scenario: 非空端口列表原样返回\n118: \n119: - **GIVEN** `ports = [{port: 8080, protocol: \"TCP\"}]`\n120: - **WHEN** `getPortsOrDefaults(ports)` 被调用\n121: - **THEN** 原样返回输入列表\n122: \n123: ### Requirement: buildEntryPoints 构建端点列表\n124: \n125: #### Scenario: 从 PodIP 和端口构建 EntryPoints\n126: \n127: - **GIVEN** `podIP = \"10.0.0.5\"`\n128:   AND `ports = [{port: 8080, protocol: \"TCP\", path: \"/\"}, {port: 8081, protocol: \"HTTP\", path: \"/api\"}]`\n129: - **WHEN** `buildEntryPoints(podIP, ports)` 被调用\n130: - **THEN** 返回 EntryPoint 列表\n131:   AND 每个 EntryPoints 的 Endpoint 格式为 `\"http://10.0.0.5:<port>\"`\n132:   AND Path 和 Protocol 正确映射\n133: \n134: ### Requirement: injectPicodAuthEnv 注入认证环境变量\n135: \n136: #### Scenario: 认证启用时注入 Secret 引用\n137: \n138: - **GIVEN** `EnableAuth = true`\n139:   AND unstructured CR 对象\n140:   AND namespace 中存在 `\"picod-router-identity\"` Secret，包含 `\"public.pem\"` 数据\n141: - **WHEN** `injectPicodAuthEnv` 被调用\n142: - **THEN** CR 的 `spec.template.spec.containers[0].env` 中注入 `PICOD_AUTH_PUBLIC_KEY` 环境变量\n143:   AND 值引用 Secret\n144: \n145: #### Scenario: 认证禁用时不修改 CR\n146: \n147: - **GIVEN** `EnableAuth = false`\n148: - **WHEN** `injectPicodAuthEnv` 被调用\n149: - **THEN** 不修改 CR 的 env 字段\n150: \n151: ### Requirement: resolvePodIP 从 Sandbox CR 解析 Pod IP\n152: \n153: #### Scenario: Pod 已分配 IP\n154: \n155: - **GIVEN** Sandbox CR 已创建且 `annotations[\"agents.x-k8s.io/sandbox-pod-name\"]` 存在\n156:   AND 对应 Pod 已运行且 `status.podIP` 不为空\n157: - **WHEN** `resolvePodIP` 被调用\n158: - **THEN** 返回 Pod 的 IP 地址\n159: \n160: #### Scenario: Pod 尚未绑定\n161: \n162: - **GIVEN** Sandbox CR 存在但未绑定 Pod（无 `sandbox-pod-name` annotation）\n163: - **WHEN** `resolvePodIP` 被调用\n164: - **THEN** 返回空字符串和错误\n165: \n166: ### Requirement: rollbackCR 清理已创建的 CR\n167: \n168: #### Scenario: 成功删除 CR\n169: \n170: - **GIVEN** 一个已创建的 CR（GVR, namespace, name 已知）\n171: - **WHEN** `rollbackCR` 被调用\n172: - **THEN** CR 被从集群中删除\n173: \n174: #### Scenario: CR 已不存在时不报错\n175: \n176: - **GIVEN** CR 已被删除\n177: - **WHEN** `rollbackCR` 被调用\n178: - **THEN** 不返回错误（IsNotFound 被忽略）\n179: \n180: ---\n181: \n182: ## R-2: Sandbox 创建 — CodeInterpreter\n183: \n184: **Scope:** `handler/sandbox_create.go` — `CreateCodeInterpreterSandbox`, `buildCodeInterpreterSandboxCR`\n185: \n186: ### Requirement: CreateCodeInterpreterSandbox 成功路径\n187: \n188: #### Scenario: 成功创建 CodeInterpreter Sandbox\n189: \n190: - **GIVEN** 有效的 CreateSandboxRequest（Kind=\"CodeInterpreter\"）\n191:   AND CodeInterpreter CR 模板存在\n192:   AND 所有依赖（DynamicClient, Store, Reconciler）可用\n193: - **WHEN** `CreateCodeInterpreterSandbox` 被调用\n194: - **THEN** 返回 HTTP 201\n195:   AND 响应包含 SessionID, SandboxID, SandboxName, EntryPoints\n196:   AND CodeInterpreter CR 已创建\n197:   AND Sandbox 信息已持久化到 Store\n198: \n199: ### Requirement: CreateCodeInterpreterSandbox 模板不存在\n200: \n201: #### Scenario: CodeInterpreter 模板未找到\n202: \n203: - **GIVEN** 目标 namespace 中不存在 CodeInterpreter CR 模板\n204: - **WHEN** `CreateCodeInterpreterSandbox` 被调用\n205: - **THEN** 返回 HTTP 404\n206:   AND 错误信息指明模板未找到\n207: \n208: ### Requirement: CreateCodeInterpreterSandbox 创建失败自动回滚\n209: \n210: #### Scenario: Sandbox CR 创建失败触发回滚\n211: \n212: - **GIVEN** CodeInterpreter 模板存在\n213:   AND 创建 Sandbox CR 时 DynamicClient 返回错误\n214: - **WHEN** `CreateCodeInterpreterSandbox` 被调用\n215: - **THEN** 返回 HTTP 500\n216:   AND 已创建的 CodeInterpreter CR 被回滚清理\n217: \n218: ### Requirement: buildCodeInterpreterSandboxCR 构建 CR\n219: \n220: #### Scenario: CR 构建包含所有必需元数据\n221: \n222: - **GIVEN** CodeInterpreter 模板 CR\n223:   AND sessionID, sandboxName, workloadName, namespace, ports 已提供\n224: - **WHEN** `buildCodeInterpreterSandboxCR` 被调用\n225: - **THEN** 返回 unstructured CR 对象和 podName\n226:   AND `metadata.labels` 包含所有必需 label（ManagedBy, SessionID, WorkloadName, SandboxName）\n227:   AND spec 从模板正确复制\n228:   AND 返回的 podName 非空\n229: \n230: ---\n231: \n232: ## R-3: Sandbox 创建 — 认证与动态客户端\n233: \n234: **Scope:** `handler/sandbox_create.go` — `getDynamicClient`; `handler/models.go` — `CreateSandboxRequest.Validate`\n235: \n236: ### Requirement: getDynamicClient 认证模式\n237: \n238: #### Scenario: 认证启用且 token 有效\n239: \n240: - **GIVEN** `EnableAuth = true`\n241:   AND 请求头中包含有效的 Authorization Bearer token\n242:   AND TokenCache.GetOrCreateUserK8sClient 返回有效的 dynamic client\n243: - **WHEN** `getDynamicClient` 被调用\n244: - **THEN** 返回 dynamic.Interface\n245:   AND 无错误\n246: \n247: #### Scenario: 认证启用但 token 缺失\n248: \n249: - **GIVEN** `EnableAuth = true`\n250:   AND 请求头中不包含 Authorization 头\n251: - **WHEN** `getDynamicClient` 被调用\n252: - **THEN** 返回 HTTP 401\n253:   AND 错误信息指明缺少认证 token\n254: \n255: #### Scenario: 认证模式禁用\n256: \n257: - **GIVEN** `EnableAuth = false`\n258: - **WHEN** `getDynamicClient` 被调用\n259: - **THEN** 返回包级别默认的 DynamicClient\n260:   AND 无错误\n261: \n262: ### Requirement: CreateSandboxRequest.Validate\n263: \n264: #### Scenario: Kind 为空\n265: \n266: - **GIVEN** `CreateSandboxRequest{Kind: \"\", Name: \"test\", Namespace: \"default\"}`\n267: - **WHEN** `Validate()` 被调用\n268: - **THEN** 返回错误，包含 `\"kind is required\"`\n269: \n270: #### Scenario: Name 为空\n271: \n272: - **GIVEN** `CreateSandboxRequest{Kind: \"AgentRuntime\", Name: \"\", Namespace: \"default\"}`\n273: - **WHEN** `Validate()` 被调用\n274: - **THEN** 返回错误，包含 `\"name is required\"`\n275: \n276: #### Scenario: Namespace 为空\n277: \n278: - **GIVEN** `CreateSandboxRequest{Kind: \"AgentRuntime\", Name: \"test\", Namespace: \"\"}`\n279: - **WHEN** `Validate()` 被调用\n280: - **THEN** 返回错误，包含 `\"namespace is required\"`\n281: \n282: #### Scenario: 所有字段有效\n283: \n284: - **GIVEN** `CreateSandboxRequest{Kind: \"AgentRuntime\", Name: \"test\", Namespace: \"default\"}`\n285: - **WHEN** `Validate()` 被调用\n286: - **THEN** 返回 nil\n287: \n288: ---\n289: \n290: ## R-4: Reconciler — AgentRuntime 调和\n291: \n292: **Scope:** `reconciler/agentruntime.go` — `reconcileAgentRuntime`, `mapConditionToStatus`, `isNotFoundError`\n293: \n294: ### Requirement: reconcileAgentRuntime 调和逻辑\n295: \n296: #### Scenario: 新建 AgentRuntime（Pending 状态）\n297: \n298: - **GIVEN** key 格式为 `\"namespace/name\"`\n299:   AND AgentRuntime CR 存在于 informer lister\n300:   AND CR 状态为 Pending（无 Ready condition）\n301:   AND Store 中无对应 session 记录\n302: - **WHEN** `reconcileAgentRuntime(key)` 被调用\n303: - **THEN** 返回 nil（无错误）\n304:   AND `metricsRecorder.IncReconcileTotal` 被调用，result=success\n305: \n306: #### Scenario: AgentRuntime 变为 Ready\n307: \n308: - **GIVEN** AgentRuntime CR 的 `status.conditions` 包含 `{type: \"Ready\", status: \"True\"}`\n309:   AND Store 中存在对应 session 记录\n310: - **WHEN** `reconcileAgentRuntime(key)` 被调用\n311: - **THEN** 更新 Store 中 SandboxInfo 的 Status 为 Running\n312:   AND 返回 nil\n313: \n314: #### Scenario: AgentRuntime 终止\n315: \n316: - **GIVEN** AgentRuntime CR 的 `status.conditions` 包含 `{type: \"Ready\", status: \"False\", reason: \"Terminated\"}`\n317:   AND Store 中存在对应 session 记录\n318: - **WHEN** `reconcileAgentRuntime(key)` 被调用\n319: - **THEN** 更新 Store 中 SandboxInfo 的 Status 为 Terminated\n320:   AND 返回 nil\n321: \n322: #### Scenario: CR 已被删除\n323: \n324: - **GIVEN** key 对应的 AgentRuntime CR 已被删除\n325: - **WHEN** `reconcileAgentRuntime(key)` 被调用\n326: - **THEN** 从 Store 中删除对应 session\n327:   AND 返回 nil（不视为错误）\n328: \n329: #### Scenario: key 格式无效\n330: \n331: - **GIVEN** `key = \"invalid-key-no-slash\"`\n332: - **WHEN** `reconcileAgentRuntime(key)` 被调用\n333: - **THEN** 返回错误，包含 `\"unexpected key format\"`\n334:   AND `metricsRecorder.IncReconcileErrors` 被调用\n335: \n336: ### Requirement: mapConditionToStatus 条件映射\n337: \n338: #### Scenario: Ready=True 映射为 running\n339: \n340: - **GIVEN** `conditions = [{type: \"Ready\", status: \"True\"}]`\n341: - **WHEN** `mapConditionToStatus(conditions)` 被调用\n342: - **THEN** 返回 `\"running\"`\n343: \n344: #### Scenario: Ready=False + Terminated 映射为 terminated\n345: \n346: - **GIVEN** `conditions = [{type: \"Ready\", status: \"False\", reason: \"Terminated\"}]`\n347: - **WHEN** `mapConditionToStatus(conditions)` 被调用\n348: - **THEN** 返回 `\"terminated\"`\n349: \n350: #### Scenario: 空条件列表映射为 pending\n351: \n352: - **GIVEN** `conditions = []`\n353: - **WHEN** `mapConditionToStatus(conditions)` 被调用\n354: - **THEN** 返回 `\"pending\"`\n355: \n356: #### Scenario: Ready=Unknown 映射为 pending\n357: \n358: - **GIVEN** `conditions = [{type: \"Ready\", status: \"Unknown\"}]`\n359: - **WHEN** `mapConditionToStatus(conditions)` 被调用\n360: - **THEN** 返回 `\"pending\"`\n361: \n362: ### Requirement: isNotFoundError 识别\n363: \n364: #### Scenario: NotFound 错误返回 true\n365: \n366: - **GIVEN** `err = errors.NewNotFound(schema.GroupResource{}, \"name\")`\n367: - **WHEN** `isNotFoundError(err)` 被调用\n368: - **THEN** 返回 true\n369: \n370: #### Scenario: 非 NotFound 错误返回 false\n371: \n372: - **GIVEN** `err = errors.NewInternalError(fmt.Errorf(\"internal\"))`\n373: - **WHEN** `isNotFoundError(err)` 被调用\n374: - **THEN** 返回 false\n375: \n376: #### Scenario: nil 错误返回 false\n377: \n378: - **GIVEN** `err = nil`\n379: - **WHEN** `isNotFoundError(err)` 被调用\n380: - **THEN** 返回 false\n381: \n382: ---\n383: \n384: ## R-5: Reconciler — CodeInterpreter 调和\n385: \n386: **Scope:** `reconciler/codeinterpreter.go` — `reconcileCodeInterpreter`\n387: \n388: ### Requirement: reconcileCodeInterpreter 调和逻辑\n389: \n390: #### Scenario: 新建 CodeInterpreter（Pending 状态）\n391: \n392: - **GIVEN** `key = \"namespace/name\"`\n393:   AND CodeInterpreter CR 存在于 lister\n394:   AND CR 状态为 Pending\n395: - **WHEN** `reconcileCodeInterpreter(key)` 被调用\n396: - **THEN** 返回 nil\n397:   AND `metricsRecorder.IncReconcileTotal(resourceTypeCodeInterpreter, resultSuccess)` 被调用\n398: \n399: #### Scenario: CodeInterpreter 变为 Ready\n400: \n401: - **GIVEN** CodeInterpreter CR 的 `status.conditions` 包含 `{type: \"Ready\", status: \"True\"}`\n402: - **WHEN** `reconcileCodeInterpreter(key)` 被调用\n403: - **THEN** 更新 Store 中 SandboxInfo 的 Status 为 Running\n404:   AND 返回 nil\n405: \n406: #### Scenario: CR 已被删除\n407: \n408: - **GIVEN** key 对应的 CodeInterpreter CR 已被删除\n409: - **WHEN** `reconcileCodeInterpreter(key)` 被调用\n410: - **THEN** 从 Store 中删除对应 session\n411:   AND 返回 nil\n412: \n413: #### Scenario: key 格式无效\n414: \n415: - **GIVEN** `key = \"no-slash\"`\n416: - **WHEN** `reconcileCodeInterpreter(key)` 被调用\n417: - **THEN** 返回错误\n418:   AND `metricsRecorder.IncReconcileErrors` 被调用\n419: \n420: ---\n421: \n422: ## R-6: Reconciler — Pod 调和\n423: \n424: **Scope:** `reconciler/pod.go` — `reconcilePod`, `buildEntryPointsFromSandboxInfo`, `extractPort`\n425: \n426: ### Requirement: reconcilePod 调和逻辑\n427: \n428: #### Scenario: Pod 已就绪并分配 IP\n429: \n430: - **GIVEN** `key = \"namespace/pod-name\"`\n431:   AND Pod 的 `status.podIP` 不为空\n432:   AND Store 中存在对应 session 记录（通过 label 匹配）\n433: - **WHEN** `reconcilePod(key)` 被调用\n434: - **THEN** 更新 Store 中 SandboxInfo 的 PodIP\n435:   AND 更新 EntryPoints 列表（基于 PodIP + 端口）\n436:   AND 返回 nil\n437: \n438: #### Scenario: Pod 未分配 IP\n439: \n440: - **GIVEN** Pod 的 `status.podIP` 为空\n441: - **WHEN** `reconcilePod(key)` 被调用\n442: - **THEN** 返回 nil（等待下次调和）\n443:   AND 不更新 Store\n444: \n445: #### Scenario: 非管理的 Pod（无 session label）\n446: \n447: - **GIVEN** Pod 的 labels 中不包含 `LabelSessionID`\n448: - **WHEN** `reconcilePod(key)` 被调用\n449: - **THEN** 返回 nil（忽略非管理 Pod）\n450: \n451: ### Requirement: buildEntryPointsFromSandboxInfo\n452: \n453: #### Scenario: 使用 PodIP 更新 EntryPoints\n454: \n455: - **GIVEN** SandboxInfo 包含 EntryPoints 模板\n456:   AND `podIP = \"10.0.0.5\"`\n457: - **WHEN** `buildEntryPointsFromSandboxInfo(info, podIP)` 被调用\n458: - **THEN** 返回 EntryPoint 列表，Endpoint 中使用 podIP 替换原有占位符\n459: \n460: ### Requirement: extractPort 提取端口\n461: \n462: #### Scenario: 从 URL 提取端口\n463: \n464: - **GIVEN** `endpoint = \"http://10.0.0.5:8080/api\"`\n465: - **WHEN** `extractPort(endpoint)` 被调用\n466: - **THEN** 返回 `\"8080\"`\n467: \n468: #### Scenario: 无端口时使用默认值\n469: \n470: - **GIVEN** `endpoint = \"10.0.0.5\"`（无端口）\n471: - **WHEN** `extractPort(endpoint)` 被调用\n472: - **THEN** 返回 `\"80\"`（默认值）\n473: \n474: ---\n475: \n476: ## R-7: Reconciler — 事件处理器\n477: \n478: **Scope:** `reconciler/event_handlers.go` — 所有 `on*Add`/`on*Update`/`on*Delete` 处理器\n479: \n480: ### Requirement: AgentRuntime 事件入队\n481: \n482: #### Scenario: AgentRuntime 新增事件\n483: \n484: - **GIVEN** 一个新增的 AgentRuntime 对象\n485: - **WHEN** `onAgentRuntimeAdd(obj)` 被调用\n486: - **THEN** `workqueue.Add(key)` 被调用，key 格式为 `\"namespace/name\"`\n487: \n488: #### Scenario: AgentRuntime 状态变化触发更新\n489: \n490: - **GIVEN** AgentRuntime 的 `status.conditions` 发生变化\n491: - **WHEN** `onAgentRuntimeUpdate(oldObj, newObj)` 被调用\n492: - **THEN** `workqueue.Add(key)` 被调用\n493: \n494: #### Scenario: AgentRuntime 非状态变化不触发更新\n495: \n496: - **GIVEN** AgentRuntime 仅 `metadata.resourceVersion` 变化，status 不变\n497: - **WHEN** `onAgentRuntimeUpdate(oldObj, newObj)` 被调用\n498: - **THEN** `workqueue.Add` 不被调用\n499: \n500: #### Scenario: AgentRuntime 删除事件\n501: \n502: - **GIVEN** 一个被删除的 AgentRuntime 对象\n503: - **WHEN** `onAgentRuntimeDelete(obj)` 被调用\n504: - **THEN** `workqueue.Add(key)` 被调用\n505: \n506: ### Requirement: CodeInterpreter 事件入队\n507: \n508: #### Scenario: CodeInterpreter Add/Update/Delete 事件\n509: \n510: - **GIVEN** 对应的 CodeInterpreter 事件（Add/Update/Delete）\n511: - **WHEN** 对应的 `onCodeInterpreter*` 处理器被调用\n512: - **THEN** `workqueue.Add(key)` 被调用\n513: \n514: ### Requirement: Pod 事件入队\n515: \n516: #### Scenario: 带 session label 的 Pod 新增\n517: \n518: - **GIVEN** 新增的 Pod 包含 `LabelSessionID` label\n519: - **WHEN** `onPodAdd(obj)` 被调用\n520: - **THEN** `workqueue.Add(podKey)` 被调用\n521: \n522: #### Scenario: 不带 session label 的 Pod 被忽略\n523: \n524: - **GIVEN** 新增的 Pod 不包含 `LabelSessionID` label\n525: - **WHEN** `onPodAdd(obj)` 被调用\n526: - **THEN** `workqueue.Add` 不被调用\n527: \n528: #### Scenario: Pod IP 变化触发更新\n529: \n530: - **GIVEN** Pod 的 `status.podIP` 从空变为非空\n531: - **WHEN** `onPodUpdate(oldObj, newObj)` 被调用\n532: - **THEN** `workqueue.Add(podKey)` 被调用\n533: \n534: #### Scenario: Pod 删除事件\n535: \n536: - **GIVEN** 一个被删除的 Pod\n537: - **WHEN** `onPodDelete(obj)` 被调用\n538: - **THEN** `workqueue.Add(podKey)` 被调用\n539: \n540: ---\n541: \n542: ## R-8: Reconciler — 工作队列与同步\n543: \n544: **Scope:** `reconciler/sync.go`, `reconciler/reconciler.go` — `syncHandler`, `processNextWorkItem`, `runWorker`, `determineResourceType`, `Enqueue`, `Run`, `WatchSandboxOnce`\n545: \n546: ### Requirement: syncHandler 同步处理\n547: \n548: #### Scenario: 成功处理并 Forget\n549: \n550: - **GIVEN** `key = \"namespace/name\"` 对应存在的 AgentRuntime\n551:   AND 调和逻辑无错误\n552: - **WHEN** `syncHandler(key)` 被调用\n553: - **THEN** 返回 nil\n554:   AND `workqueue.Forget(key)` 被调用\n555: \n556: #### Scenario: 处理失败触发重试\n557: \n558: - **GIVEN** key 对应的调和逻辑返回错误\n559: - **WHEN** `syncHandler(key)` 被调用\n560: - **THEN** 错误被返回\n561:   AND `workqueue.AddRateLimited(key)` 被调用\n562: \n563: ### Requirement: determineResourceType 资源类型判断\n564: \n565: #### Scenario: key 对应 AgentRuntime\n566: \n567: - **GIVEN** `key = \"namespace/name\"`\n568:   AND AgentRuntime lister 中存在该 key\n569: - **WHEN** `determineResourceType(key)` 被调用\n570: - **THEN** 返回 `resourceTypeAgentRuntime`\n571: \n572: #### Scenario: key 对应 CodeInterpreter\n573: \n574: - **GIVEN** `key = \"namespace/name\"`\n575:   AND AgentRuntime lister 中不存在，但 CodeInterpreter lister 中存在\n576: - **WHEN** `determineResourceType(key)` 被调用\n577: - **THEN** 返回 `resourceTypeCodeInterpreter`\n578: \n579: #### Scenario: key 对应 Pod\n580: \n581: - **GIVEN** `key = \"namespace/pod-name\"`\n582:   AND AgentRuntime 和 CodeInterpreter lister 中均不存在\n583: - **WHEN** `determineResourceType(key)` 被调用\n584: - **THEN** 返回 `resourceTypePod`\n585: \n586: ### Requirement: Enqueue 入队\n587: \n588: #### Scenario: 按 namespace/name 入队\n589: \n590: - **GIVEN** `namespace = \"default\"`, `name = \"my-sandbox\"`\n591: - **WHEN** `Enqueue(namespace, name)` 被调用\n592: - **THEN** `workqueue.Add(\"default/my-sandbox\")` 被调用\n593: \n594: ### Requirement: Run 启动与关闭\n595: \n596: #### Scenario: 启动指定数量的 worker\n597: \n598: - **GIVEN** `workers = 2`\n599:   AND cache sync 成功\n600: - **WHEN** `Run(stopCh)` 被调用\n601: - **THEN** 启动 2 个 worker goroutine\n602:   AND `metricsRecorder.SetWorkqueueDepth` 被周期性调用\n603:   AND 当 stopCh 关闭时，所有 worker 退出\n604: \n605: #### Scenario: cache sync 超时\n606: \n607: - **GIVEN** informer cache 无法在 30s 内同步\n608: - **WHEN** `Run(stopCh)` 被调用\n609: - **THEN** 记录错误日志\n610:   AND 函数返回，不启动 worker\n611: \n612: ### Requirement: WatchSandboxOnce 单次等待\n613: \n614: #### Scenario: 等待 Sandbox 就绪\n615: \n616: - **GIVEN** namespace/name 对应的 Sandbox 尚未就绪\n617: - **WHEN** `WatchSandboxOnce(namespace, name)` 被调用\n618: - **THEN** 返回一个 channel\n619:   AND 当 reconciler 处理该 key 后，channel 收到 SandboxStatus\n620:   AND channel 在收到消息后关闭\n621: \n622: #### Scenario: 重复调用相同 key\n623: \n624: - **GIVEN** 已有一个活跃的 `WatchSandboxOnce` 调用在等待\n625: - **WHEN** 再次调用 `WatchSandboxOnce(namespace, name)`（相同 key）\n626: - **THEN** 返回错误（或复用已有 channel）\n627: \n628: ### Requirement: processNextWorkItem 出队处理\n629: \n630: #### Scenario: 队列中有 item\n631: \n632: - **GIVEN** workqueue 中有一个 item\n633: - **WHEN** `processNextWorkItem()` 被调用\n634: - **THEN** 返回 true\n635:   AND item 被处理\n636:   AND `syncHandler` 被调用\n637: \n638: #### Scenario: 队列为空\n639: \n640: - **GIVEN** workqueue 为空\n641: - **WHEN** `processNextWorkItem()` 被调用\n642: - **THEN** 返回 false\n643: \n644: ---\n645: \n646: ## R-9: Lifecycle — 空闲超时与注解解析\n647: \n648: **Scope:** `handler/sandbox_lifecycle.go` — `parseIdleTimeoutFromAnnotations`, `extractIdleTimeoutFromCR`, `calculateTimeToIdle`\n649: \n650: ### Requirement: parseIdleTimeoutFromAnnotations 注解解析\n651: \n652: #### Scenario: 有效注解值\n653: \n654: - **GIVEN** `annotations = {\"runtime.agentcube.io/idle-timeout\": \"30m\"}`\n655: - **WHEN** `parseIdleTimeoutFromAnnotations(annotations, 15m)` 被调用\n656: - **THEN** 返回 `30m`\n657: \n658: #### Scenario: 无效注解值回退默认值\n659: \n660: - **GIVEN** `annotations = {\"runtime.agentcube.io/idle-timeout\": \"invalid\"}`\n661: - **WHEN** `parseIdleTimeoutFromAnnotations(annotations, 15m)` 被调用\n662: - **THEN** 返回默认值 `15m`\n663: \n664: #### Scenario: 无注解使用默认值\n665: \n666: - **GIVEN** `annotations = {}`\n667: - **WHEN** `parseIdleTimeoutFromAnnotations(annotations, 15m)` 被调用\n668: - **THEN** 返回默认值 `15m`\n669: \n670: ### Requirement: extractIdleTimeoutFromCR 从 CR 提取\n671: \n672: #### Scenario: CR 注解包含空闲超时\n673: \n674: - **GIVEN** CR 的 `metadata.annotations` 包含 `\"runtime.agentcube.io/idle-timeout\": \"20m\"`\n675: - **WHEN** `extractIdleTimeoutFromCR(cr, 15m)` 被调用\n676: - **THEN** 返回 `20m`\n677: \n678: ### Requirement: calculateTimeToIdle 计算剩余空闲时间\n679: \n680: #### Scenario: 未空闲\n681: \n682: - **GIVEN** `SandboxInfo.LastActivityAt = now - 5m`\n683:   AND `idleTimeout = 15m`\n684: - **WHEN** `calculateTimeToIdle(info, now)` 被调用\n685: - **THEN** 返回 `*time.Duration = 10m`（剩余空闲时间）\n686: \n687: #### Scenario: 已空闲超时\n688: \n689: - **GIVEN** `SandboxInfo.LastActivityAt = now - 20m`\n690:   AND `idleTimeout = 15m`\n691: - **WHEN** `calculateTimeToIdle(info, now)` 被调用\n692: - **THEN** 返回 nil（已超时）\n693: \n694: #### Scenario: 无活动时间视为已空闲\n695: \n696: - **GIVEN** `SandboxInfo.LastActivityAt` 为零值\n697: - **WHEN** `calculateTimeToIdle(info, now)` 被调用\n698: - **THEN** 返回 nil（视为已空闲）\n699: \n700: ---\n701: \n702: ## R-10: Lifecycle — GC 清理\n703: \n704: **Scope:** `handler/sandbox_lifecycle.go` — `cleanupOrphanCRs`, `cleanupGhostEntries`, `runGCCycle`\n705: \n706: ### Requirement: cleanupOrphanCRs 孤立 CR 清理\n707: \n708: #### Scenario: 发现并删除孤立 CR\n709: \n710: - **GIVEN** 集群中存在 AgentRuntime CR，其 label 中的 sessionID 在 Store 中无对应记录\n711: - **WHEN** `cleanupOrphanCRs(ctx)` 被调用\n712: - **THEN** 删除孤立 CR\n713:   AND `metricsRecorder.IncGCCleanupTotal(GRCleanupReasonOrphanCR)` 被调用\n714:   AND 返回删除数量 > 0\n715: \n716: #### Scenario: 无孤立 CR\n717: \n718: - **GIVEN** 所有 CR 的 sessionID 都能在 Store 中找到对应记录\n719: - **WHEN** `cleanupOrphanCRs(ctx)` 被调用\n720: - **THEN** 返回 0\n721:   AND 无删除操作\n722: \n723: #### Scenario: 达到扫描上限\n724: \n725: - **GIVEN** 孤立 CR 数量 > `MaxOrphanScanLimit` (100)\n726: - **WHEN** `cleanupOrphanCRs(ctx)` 被调用\n727: - **THEN** 最多删除 100 个 CR\n728:   AND 记录警告日志\n729: \n730: ### Requirement: cleanupGhostEntries 幽灵条目清理\n731: \n732: #### Scenario: 发现并清理幽灵条目\n733: \n734: - **GIVEN** Store 中存在 session 记录，但对应的 CR（AgentRuntime/CodeInterpreter）已不存在于集群\n735: - **WHEN** `cleanupGhostEntries(ctx)` 被调用\n736: - **THEN** 从 Store 中删除幽灵条目\n737:   AND `metricsRecorder.IncGCCleanupTotal(GRCleanupReasonGhostEntry)` 被调用\n738:   AND 返回清理数量\n739: \n740: #### Scenario: 无幽灵条目\n741: \n742: - **GIVEN** 所有 Store 记录对应的 CR 都存在于集群\n743: - **WHEN** `cleanupGhostEntries(ctx)` 被调用\n744: - **THEN** 返回 0\n745: \n746: ### Requirement: runGCCycle 完整 GC 周期\n747: \n748: #### Scenario: 执行完整 GC 周期\n749: \n750: - **GIVEN** 存在过期 Sandbox、空闲 Sandbox、孤立 CR、幽灵条目\n751: - **WHEN** `runGCCycle(ctx)` 被调用\n752: - **THEN** 依次执行 `cleanupExpiredSandboxes`, `cleanupOrphanCRs`, `cleanupGhostEntries`\n753:   AND `metricsRecorder.ObserveGCCycleDuration` 记录总耗时\n754:   AND 每种清理原因的 `IncGCCleanupTotal` 被正确调用\n755: \n756: ---\n757: \n758: ## R-11: Sandbox 创建 Handler — 依赖注入与构造\n759: \n760: **Scope:** `handler/sandbox_create.go` — `NewSandboxCreateHandler`, `SandboxCreateHandlerDeps`\n761: \n762: ### Requirement: NewSandboxCreateHandler 构造\n763: \n764: #### Scenario: 有效依赖构造 handler\n765: \n766: - **GIVEN** 有效的 `SandboxCreateHandlerDeps`（所有字段非 nil）\n767: - **WHEN** `NewSandboxCreateHandler(deps)` 被调用\n768: - **THEN** 返回非 nil 的 `SandboxCreateHandler`\n769:   AND handler 内部字段与 deps 一致\n770: \n771: ---\n772: \n773: ## R-12: RandString 工具函数\n774: \n775: **Scope:** `handler/sandbox_create.go` — `RandString`\n776: \n777: ### Requirement: RandString 随机字符串生成\n778: \n779: #### Scenario: 指定长度\n780: \n781: - **GIVEN** `n = 10`\n782: - **WHEN** `RandString(10)` 被调用\n783: - **THEN** 返回长度为 10 的字符串\n784:   AND 仅包含小写字母和数字\n785: \n786: #### Scenario: 随机性\n787: \n788: - **GIVEN** 无\n789: - **WHEN** 连续调用 `RandString(10)` 两次\n790: - **THEN** 两次返回值不同的概率 > 99.9%\n791: \n792: #### Scenario: 零长度\n793: \n794: - **GIVEN** `n = 0`\n795: - **WHEN** `RandString(0)` 被调用\n796: - **THEN** 返回空字符串\n797: \n798: #### Scenario: 最小长度\n799: \n800: - **GIVEN** `n = 1`\n801: - **WHEN** `RandString(1)` 被调用\n802: - **THEN** 返回长度为 1 的字符串\n803: \n804: ---\n805: \n806: ## File Structure\n807: \n808: | Path | Role |\n809: |------|------|\n810: | `pkg/workloadmanager/handler/sandbox_create_test.go` | **NEW** — Sandbox 创建流程测试 |\n811: | `pkg/workloadmanager/handler/models_test.go` | **NEW** — CreateSandboxRequest.Validate 测试 |\n812: | `pkg/workloadmanager/reconciler/agentruntime_test.go` | **NEW** — AgentRuntime 调和测试 |\n813: | `pkg/workloadmanager/reconciler/codeinterpreter_test.go` | **NEW** — CodeInterpreter 调和测试 |\n814: | `pkg/workloadmanager/reconciler/pod_test.go` | **NEW** — Pod 调和测试 |\n815: | `pkg/workloadmanager/reconciler/event_handlers_test.go` | **NEW** — 事件处理器测试 |\n816: | `pkg/workloadmanager/reconciler/sync_test.go` | **NEW** — 工作队列与同步测试 |\n817: | `pkg/workloadmanager/reconciler/reconciler_test.go` | **NEW** — Reconciler 生命周期测试 |\n818: \n819: ## Dependencies\n820: \n821: - `github.com/stretchr/testify/assert`, `github.com/stretchr/testify/require` — 断言库（已有）\n822: - `k8s.io/client-go/dynamic/fake` — 动态客户端 mock（已有）\n823: - `k8s.io/client-go/testing` — reactor 注册\n824: - `k8s.io/apimachinery/pkg/runtime` — scheme 注册\n825: - `github.com/volcano-sh/agentcube/client-go/clientset/fake` — 伪造 clientset\n826: - `github.com/gin-gonic/gin` — HTTP handler 测试（已有）\n\n(End of file - total 826 lines)\n</content>","metadata":{"preview":"# AR-038: Go 单元测试 (workloadmanager) — Delta Spec\n\n## Context\n\n- **Module:** `pkg/workloadmanager`\n- **Language:** Go\n- **Size:** L\n- **Base specs:** `deployment/client-go.md`\n\n## Scope\n\nThis delta spec defines the unit test coverage gaps for the `pkg/workloadmanager` module. Existing tests cover `handler/sandbox_delete_test.go`, `handler/sandbox_lifecycle_test.go`, `reconciler/metrics_test.go`, and `response/response_test.go`. This spec covers the **untested** code paths.\n\n---\n\n## R-1: Sandbox 创建 — AgentRuntime\n\n**Scope:** `handler/sandbox_create.go` — `CreateAgentRuntimeSandbox`, `buildAgentRuntimeSandboxCR`, `rollbackCR`, `generateSessionID`, `generateSandboxName`, `RandString`, `getPortsOrDefaults`, `buildEntryPoints`, `injectPicodAuthEnv`, `resolvePodIP`\n\n### Requirement: CreateAgentRuntimeSandbox 成功路径","truncated":false,"loaded":[]},"title":"workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/delta-spec.md","time":{"start":1775897914293,"end":1775897914301}}}}
{"type":"tool_use","timestamp":1775897915597,"sessionID":"ses_2843cba31ffeB5jipUyIoDGq0I","part":{"id":"prt_d7bc3ac450014aksxc1sjDt10J","messageID":"msg_d7bc38ef1001tJX5AWujI7CRX7","sessionID":"ses_2843cba31ffeB5jipUyIoDGq0I","type":"tool","tool":"read","callID":"call_7f779f483fcc4f29b124336b","state":{"status":"completed","input":{"filePath":"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/ci-cd/design.md"},"output":"<path>/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/ci-cd/design.md</path>\n<type>file</type>\n<content>\n1: # AgentCube CI/CD — Design\n2: \n3: Sources: `/tmp/agentcube-ref/.github/workflows/`, `/tmp/agentcube-ref/test/`, and (for Make targets) `/tmp/agentcube-ref/Makefile`.\n4: \n5: ## GitHub Actions workflows (summary table)\n6: \n7: | Filename | Workflow `name` | Trigger events | Path filters (dorny/paths-filter or notes) | Jobs | Key steps | Env vars (job/step) | Secrets |\n8: |----------|-----------------|----------------|---------------------------------------------|------|-----------|---------------------|---------|\n9: | `main.yml` | Agentcube CI Workflow | `pull_request` → `main`, `release-*` | *(none)* | `build` | Checkout; Docker Buildx setup; verify Docker; `make docker-build` | — | — |\n10: | `e2e.yml` | Agentcube E2E Tests | `pull_request` → `main`, `release-*` | *(none)* | `e2e-test` | Checkout; Go 1.23; `helm/kind-action@v1` **install_only** Kind v0.30.0, `cluster_name: agentcube-e2e`; `export ARTIFACTS_PATH=${{ github.workspace }}/e2e-logs`; `make e2e`; on failure upload `e2e-logs/`; `always` → `make e2e-clean` | `ARTIFACTS_PATH` (shell) | — |\n11: | `lint.yml` | Lint | `pull_request` → `main`, `release-*` | `lint`: `**/*.go`, `go.mod`, `go.sum`, `.golangci.yml`, `.github/workflows/lint.yml` | `golangci` | Checkout; paths-filter; if changed: Go 1.24; `make lint` | — | — |\n12: | `python-sdk-tests.yml` | Python SDK Tests | `pull_request`, `merge_group` | `sdk`: `sdk-python/**` | `python-sdk-tests` | Checkout; paths-filter; if changed: Python 3.12 in `sdk-python/`; `pip install pytest`; `pip install -e .`; `python -m pytest tests/ -v` | Default `working-directory: sdk-python` | — |\n13: | `python-lint.yml` | Python Lint | `pull_request` → `main`, `release-*` | `python`: `cmd/cli/**`, `sdk-python/**`, `example/**`, `test/**/*.py`, `pyproject.toml`, workflow self | `python_lint` | Checkout; paths-filter; if changed: Python 3.10; `pip install ruff`; `ruff check . --config pyproject.toml` | — | — |\n14: | `test-coverage.yml` | Test Coverage | `pull_request`, `merge_group`, `workflow_call` | `coverage`: `**` minus `*.md`, `*.svg`, `*.png` | `coverage` | Checkout; paths-filter; if changed: free disk space; Go 1.24; `go test` with coverage; step summary; Codecov upload; artifact `go-coverage` | `CODECOV_TOKEN` passed to Codecov action when present | `secrets.CODECOV_TOKEN` (optional; declared for `workflow_call`) |\n15: | `codegen-check.yml` | Codegen Check | `pull_request` → `main`, `release-*` | `codegen`: `pkg/apis/**`, `hack/**`, `.github/workflows/**`, `Makefile` | `codegen-check` | Checkout; paths-filter; if changed: Go 1.24.4; `make gen-check` | — | — |\n16: | `copyright-check.yml` | Copyright Check | `pull_request` → `main`, `release-*` | `copyright`: all files except `*.md`, `*.svg`, `*.png`, `docs/**`, `.github/**` | `build` | Checkout; paths-filter; if changed: `apt install moreutils`; `make gen-copyright`; `git diff --exit-code` | — | — |\n17: | `codespell.yml` | Codespell | `pull_request` → `main`, `release-*` | *(none — scans tree after temporarily removing some manifests)* | `codespell` | Backup/remove `pyproject.toml`, `package.json`, `package-lock.json`; `pip install codespell`; `codespell` with `--check-filenames`, `--skip`, `--ignore-words-list`; restore files | — | — |\n18: | `build-push-release.yml` | Build and Push Release Images | `push` → `main`; `push` tags `v*.*.*`, `v*.*.*-*` | *(none)* | `build-and-push` | Checkout; Go 1.24.4; Buildx; `docker/login-action` to `ghcr.io`; set `TAG` from ref; `make docker-buildx-push` (workload manager), `docker-buildx-push-router`, `docker-buildx-push-picod` with `IMAGE_REGISTRY` | `TAG`, `IMAGE_REGISTRY=ghcr.io/${{ github.repository_owner }}` | `GITHUB_TOKEN` (registry login) |\n19: | `dify-plugin-publish.yml` | Dify Plugin Publish | `push` tags `dify-plugin/v*` | *(none)* | `publish` | Download `dify-plugin` CLI 0.0.6; install `yq`; read `manifest.yaml`; package plugin; checkout `author/dify-plugins` with token; move `.difypkg`; branch, commit, push; `gh pr create` to `langgenius/dify-plugins` | `GH_TOKEN` on PR step | `PLUGIN_ACTION` (repo checkout + `gh`; cross-repo PR) |\n20: | `workflows-approve.yml` | Approve Workflows | `pull_request_target` types `labeled`, `synchronize` → `main`, `release-**` | *(logic: first-time contributor vs `ok-to-test` label)* | `approve` | `github-script`: list contributor PRs; if not first-time or has `ok-to-test`, list `action_required` workflow runs for SHA and approve | — | `GITHUB_TOKEN` |\n21: \n22: ### Workflow notes\n23: \n24: - **`e2e.yml`**: Uses Kind action with `install_only: true` so the cluster is created by `run_e2e.sh` (`kind create cluster`), avoiding double-creation.\n25: - **`test-coverage.yml`**: `workflow_call` declares `CODECOV_TOKEN` optional for reusable invocation; PR runs use the repo secret when configured.\n26: - **`build-push-release.yml`**: Uses older action major versions (`checkout@v3`, `setup-go@v4`, `buildx@v2`) than most other workflows.\n27: \n28: ---\n29: \n30: ## E2E test setup (`test/e2e/run_e2e.sh`)\n31: \n32: ### Kind cluster\n33: \n34: | Item | Value / behavior |\n35: |------|------------------|\n36: | Default cluster name | `E2E_CLUSTER_NAME` → `agentcube-e2e` |\n37: | Creation | `kind create cluster --name \"${E2E_CLUSTER_NAME}\"` if missing; if exists and `E2E_CLEAN_CLUSTER=true` (default), delete then recreate |\n38: | CI alignment | `.github/workflows/e2e.yml` installs Kind **v0.30.0** via `helm/kind-action@v1` (`install_only: true`) |\n39: | Skip setup | `E2E_SKIP_SETUP=true` skips `run_setup` and assumes an existing cluster |\n40: \n41: ### CRD / agent-sandbox installation\n42: \n43: Applied via `kubectl apply --validate=false` after downloading release assets (URLs built from `AGENT_SANDBOX_VERSION`, default **`v0.1.1`**):\n44: \n45: 1. `https://github.com/kubernetes-sigs/agent-sandbox/releases/download/${AGENT_SANDBOX_VERSION}/manifest.yaml`\n46: 2. `https://github.com/kubernetes-sigs/agent-sandbox/releases/download/${AGENT_SANDBOX_VERSION}/extensions.yaml`\n47: \n48: ### Images pre-pulled and loaded into Kind\n49: \n50: - `registry.k8s.io/agent-sandbox/agent-sandbox-controller:${AGENT_SANDBOX_VERSION}`\n51: - `python:3.9-slim` (echo agent workload)\n52: \n53: Local images built and loaded:\n54: \n55: - `make docker-build` → default `WORKLOAD_MANAGER_IMAGE` **`workloadmanager:latest`**\n56: - `make docker-build-router` → **`agentcube-router:latest`**\n57: - `make docker-build-picod` → **`picod:latest`**\n58: - `REDIS_IMAGE` default **`redis:7-alpine`** (Deployment + Service in namespace)\n59: \n60: ### Helm (AgentCube chart)\n61: \n62: | Item | Value |\n63: |------|--------|\n64: | Chart path | `manifests/charts/base` |\n65: | Release / namespace | `agentcube` in `AGENTCUBE_NAMESPACE` (default `agentcube`), `--create-namespace` |\n66: | Redis addr | `redis.${AGENTCUBE_NAMESPACE}.svc.cluster.local:6379`, password empty |\n67: | Workload manager image | `repository=workloadmanager`, `tag=latest` |\n68: | Router image | `repository=agentcube-router`, `tag=latest` |\n69: | Router RBAC | `router.rbac.create=true`, `router.serviceAccountName=agentcube-router` |\n70: | Extra env (JSON via `--set-json`) | Workload manager: `REDIS_PASSWORD_REQUIRED=false`, `JWT_KEY_SECRET_NAMESPACE=agentcube`; Router: `REDIS_PASSWORD_REQUIRED=false` |\n71: | Wait | `helm upgrade --install ... --wait` |\n72: \n73: ### Kubernetes fixtures applied during setup\n74: \n75: | Path | Purpose |\n76: |------|---------|\n77: | `test/e2e/echo_agent.yaml` | `AgentRuntime` `echo-agent` in `agentcube` |\n78: | Generated from `echo_agent.yaml` (sed) | `echo-agent-short-ttl` with `sessionTimeout: \"30s\"` for TTL tests |\n79: | `test/e2e/e2e_code_interpreter.yaml` | `CodeInterpreter` `e2e-code-interpreter` in `agentcube` |\n80: \n81: Warm-pool Go tests apply `e2e_code_interpreter_warmpool.yaml` at runtime (not in initial `kubectl apply` list in the shell script).\n82: \n83: ### Port forwards and health checks\n84: \n85: - Workload manager: `kubectl port-forward svc/workloadmanager` → `WORKLOAD_MANAGER_LOCAL_PORT` (default **8080**) → pod 8080\n86: - Router: `kubectl port-forward svc/agentcube-router` → `ROUTER_LOCAL_PORT` (default **8081**) → pod 8080\n87: - Readiness: `curl` to `http://localhost:${WORKLOAD_MANAGER_LOCAL_PORT}/health` and `http://localhost:${ROUTER_LOCAL_PORT}/health/live`\n88: \n89: ### Auth for tests\n90: \n91: - ServiceAccount `e2e-test` in `agentcube` + `ClusterRoleBinding` to `workloadmanager` clusterrole\n92: - API token: `kubectl create token e2e-test -n agentcube --duration=24h` → `API_TOKEN`\n93: \n94: ### Python venv for E2E\n95: \n96: - Directory: `E2E_VENV_DIR` (default `/tmp/agentcube-e2e-venv`)\n97: - `python3 -m venv`, `pip install -e ./sdk-python`, verify `import agentcube`\n98: \n99: ### Test commands invoked by `run_e2e.sh`\n100: \n101: **Go** (from repository root):\n102: \n103: ```bash\n104: WORKLOAD_MANAGER_URL=\"http://localhost:${WORKLOAD_MANAGER_LOCAL_PORT}\" \\\n105: ROUTER_URL=\"http://localhost:${ROUTER_LOCAL_PORT}\" \\\n106: API_TOKEN=$API_TOKEN \\\n107: go test -v ./test/e2e/...\n108: ```\n109: \n110: **Python** (after `cd` to `test/e2e`):\n111: \n112: ```bash\n113: WORKLOAD_MANAGER_URL=\"...\" ROUTER_URL=\"...\" API_TOKEN=$API_TOKEN \\\n114: AGENTCUBE_NAMESPACE=\"${AGENTCUBE_NAMESPACE}\" \\\n115: \"$E2E_VENV_DIR/bin/python\" test_codeinterpreter.py\n116: ```\n117: \n118: (`test_codeinterpreter.py` uses `unittest.main()` and appends `--verbose` if missing.)\n119: \n120: ### Failure artifacts\n121: \n122: On test failure, `collect_component_logs` writes under `ARTIFACTS_PATH` (CI: `${{ github.workspace }}/e2e-logs`): workload manager, router, and sandbox pod logs/describes.\n123: \n124: ---\n125: \n126: ## Test directory structure\n127: \n128: ```\n129: test/\n130: ├── OWNERS\n131: └── e2e/\n132:     ├── README.md\n133:     ├── __init__.py\n134:     ├── run_e2e.sh\n135:     ├── e2e_test.go\n136:     ├── test_codeinterpreter.py\n137:     ├── echo_agent.yaml\n138:     ├── e2e_code_interpreter.yaml\n139:     └── e2e_code_interpreter_warmpool.yaml\n140: ```\n141: \n142: ### Fixture paths (relative to repo root unless noted)\n143: \n144: | Fixture | Description |\n145: |---------|-------------|\n146: | `test/e2e/echo_agent.yaml` | Echo `AgentRuntime` for router invocation tests |\n147: | `test/e2e/e2e_code_interpreter.yaml` | Standard `CodeInterpreter` (`e2e-code-interpreter`, namespace `agentcube`) |\n148: | `test/e2e/e2e_code_interpreter_warmpool.yaml` | `CodeInterpreter` with `warmPoolSize: 2` in `default` (loaded by Go tests from **package cwd** as `e2e_code_interpreter_warmpool.yaml`) |\n149: \n150: ---\n151: \n152: ## Go test commands and flags in CI\n153: \n154: | Workflow / entrypoint | Command | Flags / notes |\n155: |------------------------|---------|----------------|\n156: | `test-coverage.yml` | `go test` | `-race -v -coverprofile=coverage.out -coverpkg=./pkg/... ./pkg/...` |\n157: | `e2e.yml` via `make e2e` → `run_e2e.sh` | `go test` | `-v ./test/e2e/...` with env `WORKLOAD_MANAGER_URL`, `ROUTER_URL`, `API_TOKEN` |\n158: \n159: ---\n160: \n161: ## Python test commands in CI\n162: \n163: | Workflow | Working dir | Command |\n164: |----------|-------------|---------|\n165: | `python-sdk-tests.yml` | `sdk-python` | `python -m pip install --upgrade pip`; `pip install pytest`; `pip install -e .`; `python -m pytest tests/ -v` |\n166: | `e2e.yml` (via `run_e2e.sh`) | Invoked from `test/e2e/` | `\"$E2E_VENV_DIR/bin/python\" test_codeinterpreter.py` (unittest, verbosity 2) |\n167: \n168: ---\n169: \n170: ## Key Make targets referenced by CI\n171: \n172: | Target | Referenced in | Role |\n173: |--------|----------------|------|\n174: | `docker-build` | `main.yml`, `run_e2e.sh` | Build workload manager image |\n175: | `docker-build-router` | `run_e2e.sh` | Build router image |\n176: | `docker-build-picod` | `run_e2e.sh` | Build picod image |\n177: | `docker-buildx-push` | `build-push-release.yml` | Push workload manager image (`IMAGE_REGISTRY`, `WORKLOAD_MANAGER_IMAGE=workloadmanager:${TAG}`) |\n178: | `docker-buildx-push-router` | `build-push-release.yml` | Push router image |\n179: | `docker-buildx-push-picod` | `build-push-release.yml` | Push picod image |\n180: | `e2e` | `e2e.yml` | Run `./test/e2e/run_e2e.sh` |\n181: | `e2e-clean` | `e2e.yml` | `kind delete cluster --name $(E2E_CLUSTER_NAME)`; `rm -rf /tmp/agent-sandbox` |\n182: | `lint` | `lint.yml` | `golangci-lint` (project default) |\n183: | `gen-check` | `codegen-check.yml` | Verify generated code up to date |\n184: | `gen-copyright` | `copyright-check.yml` | Generate copyright headers for check |\n185: \n186: ---\n187: \n188: ## Additional reference: E2E README vs script\n189: \n190: `test/e2e/README.md` states Go **1.24+** and generic “install CRDs and agent-sandbox”; the **CI workflow** pins Go **1.23** for E2E, and **run_e2e.sh** pins **agent-sandbox `v0.1.1`** by default (overridable via `AGENT_SANDBOX_VERSION`).\n\n(End of file - total 190 lines)\n</content>","metadata":{"preview":"# AgentCube CI/CD — Design\n\nSources: `/tmp/agentcube-ref/.github/workflows/`, `/tmp/agentcube-ref/test/`, and (for Make targets) `/tmp/agentcube-ref/Makefile`.\n\n## GitHub Actions workflows (summary table)\n\n| Filename | Workflow `name` | Trigger events | Path filters (dorny/paths-filter or notes) | Jobs | Key steps | Env vars (job/step) | Secrets |\n|----------|-----------------|----------------|---------------------------------------------|------|-----------|---------------------|---------|\n| `main.yml` | Agentcube CI Workflow | `pull_request` → `main`, `release-*` | *(none)* | `build` | Checkout; Docker Buildx setup; verify Docker; `make docker-build` | — | — |\n| `e2e.yml` | Agentcube E2E Tests | `pull_request` → `main`, `release-*` | *(none)* | `e2e-test` | Checkout; Go 1.23; `helm/kind-action@v1` **install_only** Kind v0.30.0, `cluster_name: agentcube-e2e`; `export ARTIFACTS_PATH=${{ github.workspace }}/e2e-logs`; `make e2e`; on failure upload `e2e-logs/`; `always` → `make e2e-clean` | `ARTIFACTS_PATH` (shell) | — |\n| `lint.yml` | Lint | `pull_request` → `main`, `release-*` | `lint`: `**/*.go`, `go.mod`, `go.sum`, `.golangci.yml`, `.github/workflows/lint.yml` | `golangci` | Checkout; paths-filter; if changed: Go 1.24; `make lint` | — | — |\n| `python-sdk-tests.yml` | Python SDK Tests | `pull_request`, `merge_group` | `sdk`: `sdk-python/**` | `python-sdk-tests` | Checkout; paths-filter; if changed: Python 3.12 in `sdk-python/`; `pip install pytest`; `pip install -e .`; `python -m pytest tests/ -v` | Default `working-directory: sdk-python` | — |\n| `python-lint.yml` | Python Lint | `pull_request` → `main`, `release-*` | `python`: `cmd/cli/**`, `sdk-python/**`, `example/**`, `test/**/*.py`, `pyproject.toml`, workflow self | `python_lint` | Checkout; paths-filter; if changed: Python 3.10; `pip install ruff`; `ruff check . --config pyproject.toml` | — | — |\n| `test-coverage.yml` | Test Coverage | `pull_request`, `merge_group`, `workflow_call` | `coverage`: `**` minus `*.md`, `*.svg`, `*.png` | `coverage` | Checkout; paths-filter; if changed: free disk space; Go 1.24; `go test` with coverage; step summary; Codecov upload; artifact `go-coverage` | `CODECOV_TOKEN` passed to Codecov action when present | `secrets.CODECOV_TOKEN` (optional; declared for `workflow_call`) |\n| `codegen-check.yml` | Codegen Check | `pull_request` → `main`, `release-*` | `codegen`: `pkg/apis/**`, `hack/**`, `.github/workflows/**`, `Makefile` | `codegen-check` | Checkout; paths-filter; if changed: Go 1.24.4; `make gen-check` | — | — |\n| `copyright-check.yml` | Copyright Check | `pull_request` → `main`, `release-*` | `copyright`: all files except `*.md`, `*.svg`, `*.png`, `docs/**`, `.github/**` | `build` | Checkout; paths-filter; if changed: `apt install moreutils`; `make gen-copyright`; `git diff --exit-code` | — | — |\n| `codespell.yml` | Codespell | `pull_request` → `main`, `release-*` | *(none — scans tree after temporarily removing some manifests)* | `codespell` | Backup/remove `pyproject.toml`, `package.json`, `package-lock.json`; `pip install codespell`; `codespell` with `--check-filenames`, `--skip`, `--ignore-words-list`; restore files | — | — |\n| `build-push-release.yml` | Build and Push Release Images | `push` → `main`; `push` tags `v*.*.*`, `v*.*.*-*` | *(none)* | `build-and-push` | Checkout; Go 1.24.4; Buildx; `docker/login-action` to `ghcr.io`; set `TAG` from ref; `make docker-buildx-push` (workload manager), `docker-buildx-push-router`, `docker-buildx-push-picod` with `IMAGE_REGISTRY` | `TAG`, `IMAGE_REGISTRY=ghcr.io/${{ github.repository_owner }}` | `GITHUB_TOKEN` (registry login) |\n| `dify-plugin-publish.yml` | Dify Plugin Publish | `push` tags `dify-plugin/v*` | *(none)* | `publish` | Download `dify-plugin` CLI 0.0.6; install `yq`; read `manifest.yaml`; package plugin; checkout `author/dify-plugins` with token; move `.difypkg`; branch, commit, push; `gh pr create` to `langgenius/dify-plugins` | `GH_TOKEN` on PR step | `PLUGIN_ACTION` (repo checkout + `gh`; cross-repo PR) |\n| `workflows-approve.yml` | Approve Workflows | `pull_request_target` types `labeled`, `synchronize` → `main`, `release-**` | *(logic: first-time contributor vs `ok-to-test` label)* | `approve` | `github-script`: list contributor PRs; if not first-time or has `ok-to-test`, list `action_required` workflow runs for SHA and approve | — | `GITHUB_TOKEN` |","truncated":false,"loaded":[]},"title":"workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/ci-cd/design.md","time":{"start":1775897915589,"end":1775897915596}}}}
{"type":"tool_use","timestamp":1775897916822,"sessionID":"ses_2843cba31ffeB5jipUyIoDGq0I","part":{"id":"prt_d7bc3b1530015MPnBKRHZQilXb","messageID":"msg_d7bc38ef1001tJX5AWujI7CRX7","sessionID":"ses_2843cba31ffeB5jipUyIoDGq0I","type":"tool","tool":"read","callID":"call_ed75cc89e87048918cb40fa4","state":{"status":"completed","input":{"filePath":"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/session-routing/design.md"},"output":"<path>/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/session-routing/design.md</path>\n<type>file</type>\n<content>\n1: # Session Routing — Design\n2: \n3: ## Module\n4: \n5: - Same repository: `github.com/volcano-sh/agentcube` (see sandbox-orchestration design for `go.mod` and versions).\n6: \n7: ## Package `github.com/volcano-sh/agentcube/pkg/router`\n8: \n9: ### Config\n10: \n11: ```go\n12: const LastActivityAnnotationKey = \"agentcube.volcano.sh/last-activity\"\n13: \n14: type Config struct {\n15:     Port                  string\n16:     Debug                 bool\n17:     EnableTLS             bool\n18:     TLSCert               string\n19:     TLSKey                string\n20:     MaxConcurrentRequests int  // 0 = unlimited at flag level; NewServer coerces to 1000\n21: }\n22: ```\n23: \n24: ### CLI flags (`cmd/router/main.go`)\n25: \n26: | Flag | Default |\n27: |------|---------|\n28: | `-port` | `8080` |\n29: | `-enable-tls` | `false` |\n30: | `-tls-cert` | `\"\"` |\n31: | `-tls-key` | `\"\"` |\n32: | `-debug` | `false` |\n33: | `-max-concurrent-requests` | `1000` (0 means unlimited per flag help; `NewServer` still sets default 1000 when `<= 0`) |\n34: \n35: ### Server struct\n36: \n37: ```go\n38: type Server struct {\n39:     config         *Config\n40:     engine         *gin.Engine\n41:     httpServer     *http.Server\n42:     sessionManager SessionManager\n43:     storeClient    store.Store\n44:     httpTransport  *http.Transport\n45:     jwtManager     *JWTManager\n46: }\n47: ```\n48: \n49: - `httpTransport`: `IdleConnTimeout: 0`, `DisableCompression: false`.\n50: - Store: `store.Storage()` for both session manager and `storeClient`.\n51: - Gin mode: `DebugMode` if `config.Debug`, else `ReleaseMode`.\n52: \n53: ### Route table\n54: \n55: | Method | Path | Middleware | Handler |\n56: |--------|------|------------|---------|\n57: | GET | `/health/live` | none | `handleHealthLive` |\n58: | GET | `/health/ready` | none | `handleHealthReady` |\n59: | GET | `/v1/namespaces/:namespace/agent-runtimes/:name/invocations/*path` | `gin.Logger`, `gin.Recovery`, `concurrencyLimitMiddleware` | `handleAgentInvoke` |\n60: | POST | same | same | `handleAgentInvoke` |\n61: | GET | `/v1/namespaces/:namespace/code-interpreters/:name/invocations/*path` | same | `handleCodeInterpreterInvoke` |\n62: | POST | same | same | `handleCodeInterpreterInvoke` |\n63: \n64: ### SessionManager interface\n65: \n66: ```go\n67: type SessionManager interface {\n68:     GetSandboxBySession(ctx context.Context, sessionID string, namespace string, name string, kind string) (*types.SandboxInfo, error)\n69: }\n70: ```\n71: \n72: ### manager implementation (`session_manager.go`)\n73: \n74: ```go\n75: type manager struct {\n76:     storeClient     store.Store\n77:     workloadMgrAddr string\n78:     httpClient      *http.Client\n79: }\n80: ```\n81: \n82: - `NewSessionManager(storeClient store.Store) (SessionManager, error)` reads `WORKLOAD_MANAGER_URL` (required).\n83: - HTTP client: `Timeout: 2 * time.Minute`; transport `MaxIdleConnsPerHost: 100`, `DisableCompression: false`; `http2.ConfigureTransports` with `ReadIdleTimeout: 30s`, `PingTimeout: 15s`.\n84: - Endpoints: `AgentRuntime` → `{WORKLOAD_MANAGER_URL}/v1/agent-runtime`; `CodeInterpreter` → `.../v1/code-interpreter`.\n85: - Request: `Content-Type: application/json`; optional `Authorization: Bearer` from `loadWorkloadManagerAuthToken()` reading `/var/run/secrets/kubernetes.io/serviceaccount/token` (trimmed); missing file → no header (warning if non-NotExist error).\n86: \n87: ### JWT (`jwt.go`)\n88: \n89: **Constants (unexported unless noted):**\n90: \n91: | Name | Value |\n92: |------|--------|\n93: | `rsaKeySize` | `2048` |\n94: | `jwtExpiration` | `5 * time.Minute` |\n95: | `IdentitySecretName` | `\"picod-router-identity\"` |\n96: | `PrivateKeyDataKey` | `\"private.pem\"` |\n97: | `PublicKeyDataKey` | `\"public.pem\"` |\n98: \n99: ```go\n100: var IdentityNamespace = \"default\" // init: AGENTCUBE_NAMESPACE if set\n101: ```\n102: \n103: **JWTManager:**\n104: \n105: ```go\n106: type JWTManager struct {\n107:     privateKey *rsa.PrivateKey\n108:     publicKey  *rsa.PublicKey\n109:     clientset  kubernetes.Interface\n110: }\n111: ```\n112: \n113: - `NewJWTManager()`: `rsa.GenerateKey(rand.Reader, rsaKeySize)`.\n114: - `GenerateToken(claims map[string]interface{}) (string, error)`:\n115:   - Base claims: `exp` = now+jwtExpiration (Unix), `iat` = now (Unix), `iss` = `\"agentcube-router\"`.\n116:   - Merges custom claims (e.g. `session_id`).\n117:   - Signing: `jwt.SigningMethodRS256`, signed with RSA private key.\n118: \n119: **Algorithm:** RS256  \n120: **Key type:** RSA 2048-bit, PKCS1 private key PEM (`RSA PRIVATE KEY`), PKIX public key PEM (`PUBLIC KEY`).\n121: \n122: **TryStoreOrLoadJWTKeySecret(ctx):**\n123: \n124: - If `clientset == nil`, try `rest.InClusterConfig()`; on failure log warning and return nil (ephemeral keys).\n125: - Else build Secret `IdentitySecretName` in `IdentityNamespace`, type `Opaque`, labels `app=agentcube`, `component=router`, data `private.pem` + `public.pem`.\n126: - Create; on `AlreadyExists`, Get secret and `loadPrivateKeyPEM`.\n127: \n128: ### Reverse proxy\n129: \n130: - `httputil.NewSingleHostReverseProxy(targetURL)`; `proxy.Transport = s.httpTransport`.\n131: - Director: sets `req.URL.Path` to normalized path, clears `RawPath`, `req.Host = targetURL.Host`, forwarding headers, `Authorization` if JWT non-empty.\n132: - `ModifyResponse`: sets `x-agentcube-session-id`.\n133: - No per-request timeout wrapper (commented-out context timeout in source).\n134: \n135: ### Concurrency middleware\n136: \n137: - Buffered channel size `config.MaxConcurrentRequests`.\n138: - `select`: send to channel or `default` → 429 + abort.\n139: \n140: ### Health JSON shapes\n141: \n142: - Live: `{\"status\":\"alive\"}`.\n143: - Ready OK: `{\"status\":\"ready\"}`.\n144: - Ready fail: `{\"status\":\"not ready\",\"error\":\"session manager not available\"}`.\n145: \n146: ### Error helper (`handleGetSandboxError`)\n147: \n148: - If `apierrors.APIStatus`: use `Status().Code` if non-zero; message from status or `err.Error()`; if code is 500, replace message with `internal server error`; respond `gin.H{\"error\": message}`.\n149: - Else 500 `{\"error\":\"internal server error\"}`.\n150: \n151: ### Environment variables\n152: \n153: | Variable | Used by |\n154: |----------|---------|\n155: | `WORKLOAD_MANAGER_URL` | Session manager (required) |\n156: | `AGENTCUBE_NAMESPACE` | JWT secret namespace (optional, default `default`) |\n157: \n158: ### Dependencies (direct use in router)\n159: \n160: - `github.com/gin-gonic/gin`, `github.com/golang-jwt/jwt/v5`, `golang.org/x/net/http2`, `k8s.io/api`, `k8s.io/apimachinery`, `k8s.io/client-go`, `k8s.io/klog/v2`, `github.com/volcano-sh/agentcube/pkg/store`, `github.com/volcano-sh/agentcube/pkg/common/types`, `github.com/volcano-sh/agentcube/pkg/api`.\n\n(End of file - total 160 lines)\n</content>","metadata":{"preview":"# Session Routing — Design\n\n## Module\n\n- Same repository: `github.com/volcano-sh/agentcube` (see sandbox-orchestration design for `go.mod` and versions).\n\n## Package `github.com/volcano-sh/agentcube/pkg/router`\n\n### Config\n\n```go\nconst LastActivityAnnotationKey = \"agentcube.volcano.sh/last-activity\"\n\ntype Config struct {\n    Port                  string\n    Debug                 bool\n    EnableTLS             bool\n    TLSCert               string\n    TLSKey                string\n    MaxConcurrentRequests int  // 0 = unlimited at flag level; NewServer coerces to 1000","truncated":false,"loaded":[]},"title":"workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/session-routing/design.md","time":{"start":1775897916814,"end":1775897916820}}}}
{"type":"tool_use","timestamp":1775897918046,"sessionID":"ses_2843cba31ffeB5jipUyIoDGq0I","part":{"id":"prt_d7bc3b61c0014KFCxCalDwS00f","messageID":"msg_d7bc38ef1001tJX5AWujI7CRX7","sessionID":"ses_2843cba31ffeB5jipUyIoDGq0I","type":"tool","tool":"read","callID":"call_c4857c8708ba497ab0ecfb8c","state":{"status":"completed","input":{"filePath":"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/idle-cleanup/design.md"},"output":"<path>/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/idle-cleanup/design.md</path>\n<type>file</type>\n<content>\n1: # Idle Cleanup — Design\n2: \n3: ## Module\n4: \n5: - `github.com/volcano-sh/agentcube` (see root `go.mod` in sandbox-orchestration design).\n6: \n7: ## Package `github.com/volcano-sh/agentcube/pkg/agentd`\n8: \n9: ### Time threshold\n10: \n11: ```go\n12: var SessionExpirationTimeout = 15 * time.Minute\n13: ```\n14: \n15: Idle expiration: `expirationTime := lastActivity.Add(SessionExpirationTimeout)`; delete when `time.Now().After(expirationTime)`.\n16: \n17: ### Annotation key\n18: \n19: The reconciler uses the same key as workload manager pod annotation for idle timeout tracking on the **Sandbox** object:\n20: \n21: - Import: `github.com/volcano-sh/agentcube/pkg/workloadmanager`\n22: - Key: `workloadmanager.LastActivityAnnotationKey` = **`\"last-activity-time\"`**\n23: \n24: (Workload manager also sets `runtime.agentcube.io/idle-timeout` on Sandbox metadata for template-driven idle configuration; **agentd** only reads `last-activity-time`.)\n25: \n26: ### Reconciler\n27: \n28: ```go\n29: package agentd\n30: \n31: type Reconciler struct {\n32:     client.Client\n33:     Scheme *runtime.Scheme\n34: }\n35: \n36: func (r *Reconciler) Reconcile(ctx context.Context, req ctrl.Request) (ctrl.Result, error)\n37: ```\n38: \n39: **Algorithm (exact behavior):**\n40: \n41: 1. `sandbox := &sandboxv1alpha1.Sandbox{}`; `Get(ctx, req.NamespacedName, sandbox)`.\n42: 2. If `errors.IsNotFound(err)` → `return ctrl.Result{}, nil`.\n43: 3. If other get error → return `ctrl.Result{}, err`.\n44: 4. `lastActivityStr, exists := sandbox.Annotations[workloadmanager.LastActivityAnnotationKey]`.\n45: 5. If `exists && lastActivityStr != \"\"`:\n46:    - `lastActivity, err := time.Parse(time.RFC3339, lastActivityStr)`\n47:    - If parse err → `return ctrl.Result{RequeueAfter: 30 * time.Second}, err`\n48:    - `expirationTime := lastActivity.Add(SessionExpirationTimeout)`\n49:    - If `time.Now().After(expirationTime)`:\n50:      - `r.Delete(ctx, sandbox)`; if err and not `IsNotFound` → `return ctrl.Result{}, err`\n51:    - Else:\n52:      - `return ctrl.Result{RequeueAfter: time.Until(expirationTime)}, nil`\n53: 6. `return ctrl.Result{}, nil`\n54: \n55: ### SetupWithManager\n56: \n57: ```go\n58: func (r *Reconciler) SetupWithManager(mgr ctrl.Manager) error {\n59:     return ctrl.NewControllerManagedBy(mgr).\n60:         For(&sandboxv1alpha1.Sandbox{}).\n61:         Complete(r)\n62: }\n63: ```\n64: \n65: ## Binary `cmd/agentd/main.go`\n66: \n67: ### Scheme registration\n68: \n69: ```go\n70: var schemeBuilder = runtime.NewScheme()\n71: \n72: func init() {\n73:     utilruntime.Must(scheme.AddToScheme(schemeBuilder))\n74:     utilruntime.Must(sandboxv1alpha1.AddToScheme(schemeBuilder))\n75: }\n76: ```\n77: \n78: ### Controller-runtime manager\n79: \n80: ```go\n81: mgr, err := ctrl.NewManager(ctrl.GetConfigOrDie(), ctrl.Options{\n82:     Scheme:                 schemeBuilder,\n83:     Metrics:                metricsserver.Options{BindAddress: \"0\"},\n84:     HealthProbeBindAddress:   \"0\",\n85: })\n86: ```\n87: \n88: ### Controller registration (duplicate of SetupWithManager pattern)\n89: \n90: ```go\n91: err = ctrl.NewControllerManagedBy(mgr).\n92:     For(&sandboxv1alpha1.Sandbox{}).\n93:     Complete(&agentd.Reconciler{\n94:         Client: mgr.GetClient(),\n95:         Scheme: mgr.GetScheme(),\n96:     })\n97: ```\n98: \n99: ### Run\n100: \n101: ```go\n102: mgr.Start(ctrl.SetupSignalHandler())\n103: ```\n104: \n105: ## Watched resources\n106: \n107: | API group | Version | Kind | Trigger |\n108: |-----------|---------|------|---------|\n109: | `agents.x-k8s.io` | `v1alpha1` | `Sandbox` | Default `For()` watch — creates, updates, deletes (per controller-runtime) |\n110: \n111: No explicit `Owns` or `Watches` — single primary resource `Sandbox`.\n112: \n113: ## Related workload-manager constants (context)\n114: \n115: From `pkg/workloadmanager` (not used by agentd reconcile logic but set when sandboxes are created):\n116: \n117: - `IdleTimeoutAnnotationKey = \"runtime.agentcube.io/idle-timeout\"` — duration string on Sandbox CR.\n118: - `LastActivityAnnotationKey = \"last-activity-time\"` — **read by agentd** for idle cleanup.\n119: \n120: ## Dependencies\n121: \n122: - `k8s.io/apimachinery/pkg/api/errors`\n123: - `k8s.io/apimachinery/pkg/runtime`\n124: - `sigs.k8s.io/agent-sandbox/api/v1alpha1`\n125: - `sigs.k8s.io/controller-runtime`\n126: - `github.com/volcano-sh/agentcube/pkg/workloadmanager` (annotation key only)\n\n(End of file - total 126 lines)\n</content>","metadata":{"preview":"# Idle Cleanup — Design\n\n## Module\n\n- `github.com/volcano-sh/agentcube` (see root `go.mod` in sandbox-orchestration design).\n\n## Package `github.com/volcano-sh/agentcube/pkg/agentd`\n\n### Time threshold\n\n```go\nvar SessionExpirationTimeout = 15 * time.Minute\n```\n\nIdle expiration: `expirationTime := lastActivity.Add(SessionExpirationTimeout)`; delete when `time.Now().After(expirationTime)`.\n\n### Annotation key\n\nThe reconciler uses the same key as workload manager pod annotation for idle timeout tracking on the **Sandbox** object:\n","truncated":false,"loaded":[]},"title":"workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/idle-cleanup/design.md","time":{"start":1775897918036,"end":1775897918044}}}}
